# Third-party VarFunction discovery file.
#
# Plug-ins distributing custom VarFunction implementations should ship a similar file
# under their own META-INF/services/ folder.
#
# Built-in functions ship via Builder.defaultFunctions() (programmatic registration in
# VarResolver.DEFAULT), NOT via this file — listing them here would double-register them.
#
# Resolution priority (later wins on name collision per OQA #3):
#
#   built-in catalog < ServiceLoader entries < explicit Builder.functions(...) calls
#
# So third-party entries here automatically override built-ins on name collision.
